Were this:
sed -i "s/$grp/$grp$delim$2/g" ${IPKG_INSTROOT}/etc/group
creates /etc/groupRANDOM and renames it to /etc/group afterwards
if i understand correctly then:
sed -i'' "s/$grp/$grp$delim$2/g" ${IPKG_INSTROOT}/etc/group
fixes it
